### Step 4: Validate

Run these commands in order:

1. `dotnet build sdk/computefleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeFleet/`
2. `dotnet test sdk/computefleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeFleet/ --filter TestCategory!=Live`
3. `eng/scripts/Update-Snippets.ps1 computefleet` — injects the `#region Snippet:` code from the new test file into the README placeholders; check `git diff` to confirm README was updated
4. `eng/scripts/Export-API.ps1 computefleet` — regenerates API listing files (no new public surface expected, but run to ensure consistency)
5. `dotnet format sdk/computefleet/Azure.ResourceManager.ComputeFleet/` — ensures consistent formatting

